{"tid":87619,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【變態教師】學生冇做功課 竟要家長罰企幾粒鐘","createTime":"2017-01-20T03:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T11:33:22.000Z","uid":48093,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c905039d975a2ba3b37ef140d23a7e3b72f98e","tid":87619,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170120/large/1484878169_4632.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170120%2Flarge%2F1484878169_4632.jpg&h=17c2b99f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一人做事一人當，但在黑龍江大慶市的一間中學，學生犯錯竟要家長受罰。當地一名在企業任科級幹部的家長，因為兒子沒做功課，被老師叫到學校罰企兩小時，讓他感到無地自容。<br />\n<br />\n這名科級幹部姓張，前日他接到學校的電話，要他到學校與兒子的老師見面。見面時老師指他的兒子未做好功課，還差兩份未做，「依規定」要他代兒子罰企。<br />\n張於是在校內走廊與其他家長罰企，覺得無地自容，他與其他家長一同互相安慰，稱子女不做功課，老師不敢打不敢罵，就只能找家長來罰企。<br />\n可是，不少家長都覺得要代學生受罰，實在不能接受，認為教師應該先與家長勤溝通，針對孩子的性格特點，進行教育。"},{"pid":"884a7d206ac9d7f4f5963ddc8590fc5e69b41818","tid":87619,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816bf1f34e74782f43011ab230a5a7e60a2382ae","tid":87619,"uid":31901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:34:50.000Z","msg":"做得好阿 唔識教仔緊係罰老豆老母啦"},{"pid":"e76aba301338b95fe27fdd7f952b19bb6d07c266","tid":87619,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得好阿 唔識教仔緊係罰老豆老母啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好鬼醒個老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ff92351106f1130c2ead3f0538d83fdb977d28","tid":87619,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做得好阿 唔識教仔緊係罰老豆老母啦</blockquot